snippet.title: Gameplay teaser || Tomorrow The Game
snippet.description:
Tomorrow The Game is a horror game based on the video clip by Jaye. In this game, the player has to free a bunny from the hands of the feared clown that haunts this abandoned station. Be careful though, because Jaye might just find you, and when he does, you won't survive.

Get the game here:
https://tomorrow-the-game.itch.io/tomorrow


Link to music video:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mvPAlzLYfzQ
